title: Dadra and Nagar Haveli football team
text:
The Dadra and Nagar Haveli is an Indian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team representing <a href="Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli">Dadra and Nagar Haveli</a> district of the union territory of <a href="Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu">Dadra and Nagar Haveli and Daman and Diu</a> in the <a href="Santosh%20Trophy">Santosh Trophy</a>.
They have never won the Santosh trophy.
